page.content: This project was undertaken by a small Social Studies group from Sandy Upper.Mrs Tyrrell the groups tutor would like to thank everybody who helped in the production of this project{ {Stephen Ayers,Darryl Clark,Simon {Clarke,David Cook,Paul Darlow,Paula {Egg-Hope,Stephen Geers,Stewart {Hart,Stephen Pantry,Denise {Raffaelli,Simon Smith,Tom Smith,Teresa {Woolnough.
